videos.description: Deng Adel dribbles inside the paint and puts in a tricky layup in the first half against Bryant College.
videos.headline: Louisville's Adel drives inside for and -1

videos.description: Deng Adel passes to Ryan Spalding who finishes at the rim with a sweet one-handed dunk at the end of the first half.
videos.headline: Louisville's Spalding steals and hits an alley-oop slam

videos.description: Dino Gaudio and Kevin Fitzgerald agree the toughest matchup for Louisville in the Gotham Classic is against Memphis on Saturday December 16 at Madison Square Garden.
videos.headline: Louisville prepares to take on Memphis

videos.description: Deng Adel sinks a nice 3-pointer from the wing to extend the Cardinals' lead to 71-42 against the Bulldogs in the second half.
videos.headline: Adel knocks in a triple for Louisville

videos.description: Malik Williams rebounds and hits a layup at the end of the second half against Bryant University. The Cardinals go on to win 102-59 against the Bulldogs on Monday night.
videos.headline: Williams' layup adds to Louisville's lead
